data.purpose: AKUMS DRUGS AND PHARMACEUTICALS LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 09-Nov-2024 to inter-alia consider and approve the Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the Quarterly ended September 2024 .
